1
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,800
What is inside my belly?

2
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,200
Get out! Get out of me!

3
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,520
What is it?

4
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,160
Get out!

5
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:32,560
No!

6
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,840
Who are you?

7
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,800
Get out!

8
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,400
Who are you?

9
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:57,520
Come out!

10
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,720
Get out!

11
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,600
Madam! Madam!

12
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,520
What is wrong?

13
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,560
My husband.

14
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,520
There is a ghost!

15
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,520
He has returned.

16
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,960
He has returned.

17
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,440
He has returned.

18
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,120
There are no ghosts. Where would a ghost come from?

19
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:10,760
Listen to me.

20
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,280
Hurry and drink this soothing medicine.

21
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,160
Have a good sleep, and you will be fine.

22
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:15,720
I cannot sleep.

23
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,720
He... he is right inside my belly.

24
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,160
He is right inside my belly.

25
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,640
He wants to come out.

26
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,480
Please, stop causing more trouble.

27
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,760
A clear conscience fears no ghosts.

28
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,200
You...

29
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,040
Madam.

30
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,560
Jin'er was stillborn.

31
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,960
Was it you?

32
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,360
What do you mean?

33
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,520
We have been husband and wife for decades.

34
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,240
You suspect me?

35
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,800
No, no, no, no.

36
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,360
How could I suspect you?

37
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,960
Come, drink the medicine.

38
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,880
I will not drink it.

39
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,760
I know that after all these barren years...

40
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,120
...you blame me.

41
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,600
But for so many years...

42
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,800
...I have done so much for this family.

43
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,920
Yet in your heart, there is only that Witch.

44
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,600
Do you want to divorce me now?

45
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:08,040
Is that why you are falsely accusing me?

46
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:08,560
Madam.

47
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,920
I have never suspected you.

48
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,760
The manor has not been peaceful lately.

49
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,840
Please do not make a scene.

50
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:14,480
Rest well.

51
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,320
I will fetch another dose of medicine.

52
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,200
You feed me medicine every day.

53
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,520
What are your intentions?

54
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,960
You all want to kill me.

55
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,520
You all want to kill me!

56
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:23,760
Li Niangu!

57
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,800
You might as well just kill me!

58
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,120
End it all once and for all.

59
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,680
So you can elevate that Seductress to my place.

60
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,880
Madam! Madam, do not!

61
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,080
Do not!

62
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,680
You, take this to the side room.

63
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,120
Hurry up, there's another one.

64
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,640
Quick, quick, quick! And you!

65
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:41,800
Go over there.

66
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,160
Hurry and bring me that water.

67
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,520
Do you hear me?

68
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:43,800
Yes, yes, yes.

69
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:44,680
Hurry up!

70
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:45,960
Take more.

71
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,640
You, move this table over there.

72
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,120
Why are you all standing around?

73
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,520
Get moving, get moving!

74
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,560
Hurry, everyone is waiting!

75
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:52,840
Quick, quick, quick!

76
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,280
You two, go over there, over there.

77
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,120
What's so interesting on the street?

78
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,040
Do you also think...

79
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,920
...there is something wrong with Li Manor?

80
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:01,720
Mm-hmm.

81
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:07,120
Li Manor is exceptionally busy today.

82
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,680
A coffin.

83
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,240
Li's wife, Madam Zhang, was frightened.

84
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,520
The dead infant was dug up.

85
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:18,360
Who is this coffin prepared for now?

86
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,600
Be careful.

87
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,440
Did you hear that?

88
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,160
Hurry.

89
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,480
Interesting.

90
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,160
Let's go take a look.

91
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,480
My Lord.

92
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:30,720
What should we do about this?

93
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:31,920
This guy...

94
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:34,280
...ate half my monthly salary by himself.

95
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,960
I really can't do anything about him.

96
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,280
Madam Zhang died a sudden, violent death.

97
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,960
This matter is becoming increasingly bizarre.

98
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:45,760
Could it be...

99
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,280
...that there really are ghosts?

100
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:50,080
With me here...

101
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,280
...what are you afraid of?

102
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,920
The more bizarre things get...

103
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,360
...the more afraid Li Niangu becomes.

104
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:57,360
That is only to our advantage.

105
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,960
Then regarding this Ritual...

106
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,160
...we will rely on you, Divine Master.

107
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,240
Rest assured.

108
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,360
Will you need laborers for the burial?

109
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:06,800
No need.

110
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:07,800
Thank you.

111
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:08,560
Let's go.

112
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,120
Someone has passed away...

113
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,400
...yet they set up a ritual hall instead of a mourning hall.

114
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,760
Conducting a Ritual instead of funeral arrangements.

115
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,280
Interesting.

116
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,240
Acting Vice Minister.

117
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,760
Please forgive my lack of manners.

118
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:31,400
Mm.

119
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:32,800
This is...

120
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:34,920
...my wife.

121
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,600
She has just passed away.

122
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,640
Since we are here...

123
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,000
...let us pay our respects together.

124
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,200
That won't be necessary.

125
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,160
Do not...

126
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,600
...taint yourself with that bad luck.

127
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:47,440
Bad luck?

128
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,920
Everyone must die eventually.

129
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,000
Why speak of bad luck?

130
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,680
My Lords, you do not know the details.

131
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,480
My wife...

132
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,840
...committed suicide by throat-slitting.

133
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,080
Suicide by throat-slitting?

134
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,640
Why?

135
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,720
My wife has been repeatedly frightened recently.

136
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,640
She was restless and anxious.

137
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,400
Her spirit could not take it.

138
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:10,520
Last night, it was as if she were possessed.

139
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,440
Do you not find this matter suspicious, my Lord?

140
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,480
To conclude Madam was merely frightened?

141
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,160
Suspicious?

142
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,600
Where is the body?

143
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:24,920
My Lord...

144
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:26,720
...follow me.

145
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:29,760
Please.

146
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,080
My Lord.

147
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,520
I would not dare speak falsely.

148
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,600
Please look.

149
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,000
The sharp weapon entered here.

150
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,080
Slitting the neck.

151
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,120
Observe that the wound is deep at the start...

152
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,160
...and gradually becomes shallower.

153
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,360
This is because blood loss and pain intensified...

154
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,520
...causing the strength to gradually weaken.

155
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,600
It matches the characteristics of suicide by throat-slitting.

156
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,280
At first glance...

157
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,120
...there are no signs of poisoning.

158
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,520
My Lord

159
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,000
Look

160
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:45,800
I told you so

161
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,480
An infant's skull

162
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,880
Shouldn't scare someone like this

163
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,680
But Madam Zhang's pupils are dilated and bleeding

164
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,440
It is indeed a sign of death by fright

165
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,840
Then there must be another reason

166
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,480
However, the stillborn in Hong Xiu's womb

167
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,640
Must be related to Madam Zhang

168
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:01,760
Using this skull to lure out the ghost in Madam Zhang's heart

169
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,920
Was it Hong Xiu

170
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,080
Or someone else

171
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,240
Madam Zhang's body needs further examination

172
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,840
Truly a pair of master hands

173
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,720
To make this skull so realistic

174
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:11,640
But

175
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,720
Do children have this many teeth?

176
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,080
Are you questioning my skills?

177
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,040
How about I make one for you next time?

178
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:19,560
No need, thanks

179
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,040
Really

180
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,120
Just let me carve one

181
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,200
Next time I'll help you

182
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:24,560
No need

183
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:25,440
No

184
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,000
No, no, no

185
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,240
You

186
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:26,840
Don't be so polite

187
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,560
Are we still investigating today or not?

188
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,440
Close doors and windows

189
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,320
Guard against thieves

190
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:39,240
Close doors and windows

191
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,200
Guard against thieves

192
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:02,720
Qin Shitou

193
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,640
You are Qin Shitou

194
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,240
Ghost!

195
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,680
There's a ghost!
